Get status of firewalld:
# firewall-cmd --state
running

Reload configuration while maintaining state of active connections:
# firewall-cmd --reload

Save active runtime configuration to permanant configuration:
# firewall-cmd --runtime-to-permanent

Show active runtime configuration of a zone (interfaces, services, ports, etc.):
# firewall-cmd [--permanent] [--zone=<zonename>] --list-all
